@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mbuoip(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.96 / v2 + 0.05)) / (wp.cos(v2 + 0.56) + 0.24))
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = wp.cos(((v2 + 0.86 * tmp + 0.54) + wp.sin(v2 + 0.07)))
    tmp = (0.40 - wp.exp(tmp))
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.cos(v1 + 0.81) * (v2 + 0.89 * v0 + 0.32)))
    v0 = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.64) + (v1 + 0.43 - tmp + 0.39)) - ((tmp + 0.41 - v1 + 0.90) - wp.exp(v1 + 0.40)))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.sin(wp.exp(v2 + 0.07)))
    data[tid] = v0
